  "acceptance": [
    "The implementation identifies the source-of-truth skill templates for the ATM entry path and updates those templates first.",
    "The governance-router remains thin: it points agents to `next`, playbook, and specialist skills instead of embedding a full taskflow manual.",
    "The durable checklist appears in the appropriate entry or specialist skill surface so Captain, dispatch, handoff, evidence, and first-layer governance work consume the same rule set.",
